					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7098152#post-3929587</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7098152/scp-4097#post-3929587</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 26 Aug 2018 16:23:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MemeFury</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4001485</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I really enjoyed this SCP, however I think the article needs run through with a fine toothed comb; there was a lot of very small but noticable flaws, like wrong punctuation or a missing word, and the log at the end sounded way too casual imo (also I think having You be a character in it is sorta silly, as it breaks the immersion of the article. Having it be a junior researcher or something would help).</p> <p>However this article is really damn cool and I like it for what it is, and it gets my +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
